parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.This is it Diana. What do you think?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrOp.Quite fascinating and well hidden in this cove.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaOp.It’s hard to tell what this is. But it appears to be old enough to correlate with the Tikpak creating it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.Any clue how to get past it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx<.I can’t move the rock. It’s way too big.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.How the hell are we going to get back?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.In that rough water!? The tide will pull us out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe.We can wait for the tide change.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.That’s hours from now... It’ll be pitch black by then.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiSaEx.We have no choice. We’ll have to wait till morning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Can we survive in the jungle overnight?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlOp.Are you kidding me? Of course we can. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.Your Father and I have been in much worse situations than this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I wish I had known him the way you did. It sounds like you had a lot of fun adventures with him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrEx.Come on 1Hero. Find some kindling. We need to get a fire going to keep warm after sunset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrOp.Rest up 1Hero. We’ve got our work cut out for us tomorrow morning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaOp.With a little luck, perhaps this will be my last.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I can’t believe you’d want this to be your last adventure. For me, I’m just getting started.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaOp.But eventually luck will catch up with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.What happened Diana? What made you change your tune?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiSaOp.I got caught up with the wrong people.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiSaEx.I was tricked into stealing a valuable treasure for a very bad man.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaOp.So I decided to take it for myself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnOp.I got caught. Now I have a debt to pay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.So, that guy who took the Tikpak treasure in the crate...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.Yes 1Hero. He’s a henchman for my former employer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrEx.I’ve made a good deal. It’s time to stop running.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrEx.It’s not a big deal 1Hero. And now that you’re here you’re helping me repay my debt faster than scheduled.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.Your talismans are well sought after by illegal art collectors.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I’m glad I can help. It’s too bad you’re not keeping the profits.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.If we find the Tikpak treasure I’ll have no more worries.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrOp.I can retire and leave it all behind me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.Be careful who you meet in your journeys 1Hero. This world is filled with liars and thieves.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlEx.The only thing your Father ever stole was credit. He never wanted the treasure, just the fame.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.But you never hooked up with him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlOp.Despite his many attempts to make a pass at me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Diana. Why’d you kiss me on top of Mount Vedra?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaEx.No way! Of course I want to kiss you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlOp.I sure could use a nice massage. Are you up for it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlOp.Careful 1Hero. Let’s see how far you can push your luck tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "You’ve unlocked new lures at the Bait Shop!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.The rock here looks weak and crumbly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "This is the main valley of the maca plant. Come back here whenever you need more.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlOp.What’s wrong 1Hero? Am I too much for you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFrOp.Well. What are we waiting for? Let’s see what’s on the other side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I can see something just out of reach.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I can see something just out of reach.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnEx.Corn! There’s no back entrance. We have to go back into the cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiShOp.1Hero!? What are you doing out here so late? And who is your... friend?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaCl.Oh, hey Michael... This is my uncle... Uhhh... Uncle Bob.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoOp.Well you two shouldn’t be out here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Uhh.. What he means to say is that we’re looking for bigfoot... I saw him earlier!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiShEx.You did!? I was just out here looking myself. I read that bigfoot feeds at night...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoEx.Which makes it hard to find them, because the jaguars also feed at night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoOp.Speaking of which. You better get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Wait... Michael. Uhhh... Uncle Bob here is an expert bigfoot hunter and he specializes in night stalking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CoAnDe.I have very big feet. No jaguar scares me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoOp.You all need to head back. Where is your canoe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.I better get back to tracking the bigfoot. I think I’m getting close.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.Corn! Let’s go back into the cave. You heard him. There are jaguars feeding at night!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CoAnEx.Find backdoor of cave first. Then we will be in cave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Shit. He’s not going into the deep jungle is he?");
